input: Subject: A grand piano; Characteristics: polished black surface with open lid; Timing and lighting: evening with spotlight; Background: elegant concert hall; Feeling: sophisticated and inspiring.
output: A gleaming, ebony grand piano sits center stage under a warm spotlight illuminating its open lid. Silhouetted against the backdrop of an opulent concert hall, filled with plush velvet seats and ornate chandeliers, the image captures the stillness before a performance. Bathed in the dramatic glow of the evening, the scene evokes a profound sense of sophistication and inspiration, promising a musical masterpiece yet to unfold.
